---
title: Pepper and Pork Stir-Fry with Green Onion Rice
description: It's a mixed veggie bonanza! Zucchini and sweet bell peppers get tossed with garlicky pork and drizzled with a glossy, umami-packed hoisin sauce! Green onion rice makes the perfect pedestal for these fine flavours to rest on!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saute-de-porc-et-de-poivrons-8282d097.jpg
